COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 6:27AM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.5 thousand have died.

In the last day, 176 new infections were reported and 3 deaths. This is trending upwards.

Fortunately, 44.9 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 79.6% have their 1st shot and 55.5% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 8 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~20 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Nov-29 and fully vaccinated by Aug-18. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
